comment: Vucevic (ORL) sets the screen on Dragic (MIA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
After communicating with the Replay Center, Ibaka (ORL) is assessed a common foul.
Ibaka (ORL) makes contact to Dragic's (MIA) body that affects his shot attempt in transition.
[Incidental or immaterial] Johnson (MIA) never fully clears the lane and is not actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Johnson (MIA) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Fournier (ORL) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Johnson (MIA) legally contests Fournier's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
Whiteside (MIA) makes legal contact with the ball.
Ibaka (ORL) maintains legal guarding position on the driving shot attempt by Johnson (MIA).
Johnson (MIA) commits a take foul on Vucevic (ORL).
Fournier (ORL) legally contests Waiters' (MIA) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Johnson (MIA) commits a take foul on Ibaka (ORL).
